verbose_text: Following the participation of some of us to a preliminary collaborative study that measured the levels of Coenzyme Q10 in muscle in a series of patients affected by ICA with onset in childhood of unknown cause, XREF_BIBR after exclusion of known causes of ICA we decided to systematically carry out a muscle biopsy in patients with non syndromic CA or CHA associated to " pure " cerebellar atrophy in order to verify the impact of the muscle biopsy examination in the diagnosis of this group of disorders.
